## 📊 Performance Considerations

### Optimization Strategies

1. **Virtual Scrolling** - For 100+ tasks
```typescript
import { FixedSizeList } from 'react-window';

<FixedSizeList
  height={600}
  itemCount={tasks.length}
  itemSize={40}
>
  {({ index, style }) => (
    <GanttRow task={tasks[index]} style={style} />
  )}
</FixedSizeList>
```

2. **Memoization** - Prevent re-renders
```typescript
const GanttBar = React.memo(({ task }) => {
  // ... render logic
}, (prevProps, nextProps) => {
  return prevProps.task.id === nextProps.task.id &&
         prevProps.task.startDate === nextProps.task.startDate &&
         prevProps.task.dueDate === nextProps.task.dueDate;
});
```

3. **Debounced Calculations** - For critical path
```typescript
const debouncedCalculateCriticalPath = useMemo(
  () => debounce(calculateCriticalPath, 300),
  []
);

useEffect(() => {
  debouncedCalculateCriticalPath(tasks);
}, [tasks]);
```

